This folder will contain the files that describe, define, setup the game and
its content.

It would be nice to have some of these files written in the Lua scripting language.
This would allow quicker development, because the scrpits could be loaded on demand
without re-compiling everything.


Example of what these files will contain (Psuedo-code):
//pirate.cpp
#include "engine/player.cpp" 
#include "engine/animation.cpp"
#include "engine/physics.cpp"

class Pirate : public Player
{
	Pirate()
	{
		maxVelocity = 100;
		AnimationComponent.add( sword_attack, pirate.png, 40, 60 );
		ActionComponent.add( sword_attack, "attack" );
	}
	void update()
	{
		//do something awesome
		//then call player's update function
		Player::update();
	}
};
